{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">我的关键业务是项目策划执行、宣传推广。</span><br></p><p>目前接触新项目，对于我来说，因为负责执行多个项目，有丰富的经验，但策划方面潜力还未得到发挥。</p><p>因此，我计划这样提升策划业务：</p><p>1.在网上找出项目策划的案例，整理出策划思路和框架。</p><p>2.用这些思路和框架做策划练习，策划多个项目。</p><p>3.与同事、领导讨论策划思路和框架的高度和可行性，进而纠正自己的思路和框架。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7948,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492501988000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Elva","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoFaxYzCOkAgT6U2G0vGpXUa0F8N8eibrdQDFDpDsIQR0o4LFlkibaV2e9sqVQWTSnESkEN3QcQNcXz/0","content":"公司被收购了，现在我负责的业务非常尴尬，几乎每天都咩有什么确定的事情可以做，就做些一些固定的事务，心里有点恐慌，所以看书学点东西。各位有啥指导啊~","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7360,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491557056000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoPsccICKmhqibTHZ3c6PRPlXKQOMsQGCZVTGNkMa0625BIPiaGC4xAlvbRSOslvms4H38dWlfyorDL/0","content":"工作中一直用的\uD83D\uDE04","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7262,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491434053000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lanlan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","content":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 以前曾经听说过二八法则，这个法则其实应用很广，商业领域、人际关系领域、甚至生活中很多方面都可以运用。在我目前的业务中，能够带来更多收益的有：</p><p>1、X产品的持续升级和维护----收益包括经济方面和未来该产品市场的持续占有；</p><p>2、团队合作项目的研发；</p><p>3、项目管理工作；</p><p>4、工作机会中专业领域的拓展和深入；</p><p><br></p><p>潜力最大的业务包括：</p><p>1、团队合作项目的研发----将接触到新的领域，有更多机会；</p><p>2、项目管理工作----对现有团队的管理，持续提高团队能力和效率；</p><p>3、工作机会中专业领域的拓展和深入----是对未来5-10年的准备，可带来长远利益。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7249,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491396210000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"影子（one life one liver）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay7P6qrmu6EFgMxv9yByicqqSVMrdaJoMs4TEyich23rD3ictMbhBfngbwia0x0G3qzXEM5ib5SQ8bx5vQ/0","content":"把精力集中于少数疑难关键问题上，可以提升自己的思维和知识，收获到认可和个人品牌。<div>方案：精力集中于有影响力的客户那里，通过美誉度提高自己的影响力。让自己的服务超值且美好，使用追求和吸引两个法则，让服务实现自传播属性，好到让人上瘾，让人觉得尊贵和安全。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7127,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491194084000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-30","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"收益更大的业务：\n外部业务：\n1.利润方面-危重程度较高的病人\n2.成就感-危重疑难的病人\n3.口碑-术后较轻的病人\n\n内部业务：\n1.利益晋升-科研工作\n2.利润收入-会诊讲课\n3.口碑成就感-诊治讲课\n4.建立品牌-科研团队\n\n潜力最大的业务：\n建立科研团队，主攻危重程度较高的核心方向，并以此展开临床诊疗，会诊相关病人，在行业协会中展示并演讲推广，带教下级医生参观学习\n\n综合考虑，制定相关计划如下：\n1.确定研究方向(危重程度较高的核心业务)\n2.增强相关核心资源-专业知识，科研能力，演讲及团队管理能力\n3.执行计划并尽早有科研产出\n4.行业协会及患者群中推广展示，建立品牌并获得最大收益","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6098,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490880748000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"目前主要工作里面的宣传一块，其实学到的东西和认识的有趣的人是最多的，但是目前给他的时间和重视程度其实是不太够的，主要原因也是因为事物性的杂七杂八的事情耗费了很多时间和精力，而且每项工作都是支撑性的，后序等待的同事也要催促。\n\n按照这个法则，适当在主营业务上作倾斜，在事务性工作上动脑筋，优化流程或者委托办理，为主营业务压出点时间。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6533,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490769426000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
